PROBLEM STATEMENT
input1= no of rows(5)
input2= weight of head row(10)
input3=weight increment for subsequent rows(2)
op =10+(12+12)+(14+14+14)+(16+16+16+16)+(18+18+18+18+18)=230

pattern looks like
*
**
***
****
*****


CODE
import java.util.*;
class main{
public int totalHillWeight(int input1,int input2,int input3){
int sum=input2,s=input2;
    for(int i=2;i<=input1;i++){
       s=s+input3;
       sum+=i*s;
    }
    return sum;
}
}
